MimeType=video/x-flv

Bitrate=256

[audio only 192 kbit]
Cmd=-threads {threads} {offset} {realtime} -i "{infile}" -f flv -vn -acodec libmp3lame -ab 192k -ar 44100 -ac 2 -y -threads {threads} "{outfile}"

MimeType=audio/x-flv
